# Allowlist context. The image is built from a prebuilt static-musl binary, so it
# needs ONLY that binary + the external os-templates/ data. Everything else
# (crates/ source, target/, .git/, the embedded static/+templates/, node_modules,
# docs, …) only bloats the build context and churns the cache key — exclude it all,
# then re-include exactly what the Dockerfile COPYs.
*
!dragonfly-*
!os-templates
